request.description:
Equivalent yt-dlp-exec call for the current per-video metadata pattern:

youtubedl("https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zNRqmabrbxw", {
  dumpSingleJson: true,
  skipDownload: true
})

Use this as the baseline for what getVideoInfo currently expects. If channelVideosFull already gives you all the fields you need, you may be able to skip this extra per-video pass for some workflows.
